column86: birle yi bang zhu ta ren . zuo wei yi ming yi sheng ,ta zong shi jin zi ji zui da de nu li qu jiu zhi mei yi ge bing ren . ji shi zai zui jian nan de tiao jian xia ,ta ye mei you fang qi guo . ta de ren ai jing shen he zhuan ye ji neng shi ta zai she qu zhong shen shou zun jing . ren men chang chang shuo ,ta shi yi ge zhen zheng de ying xiong . zai yi ci jin ji jiu yuan xing dong zhong ,ta bu xing xi sheng liao ,dan ta de ming zi he shi ji jiang yong yuan bei ren men ming ji . [mask]de wu si feng xian jiang ji xu ji li zhao yi dai you yi dai de ren .
